<lefticon>undefined</lefticon>
<righticon>orchestration</righticon>
<column>OOCI</column>
<textHTML>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Compile all created resources by Stage 1 groups into one master resource &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Post it on the course management system for students to review and use for study&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</textHTML>
